{"type": "article", "id": 21972, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23187, "name": "harto"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 23188, "name": "Lignum Bike Company"}, {"id": 23189, "name": "Moreno Ratti"}, {"id": 23190, "name": "haim evgi"}, {"id": 23191, "name": "Yuta Takahashi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 90, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135014yebtivFhOkNX4UJV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p>\n<h2>Suspended Collection by Moreno Ratti</h2>\n<p>意大利设计师 Moreno Ratti 擅长用大理石创作，这套花瓶和果盘系列来自他出身地 carrara（卡拉拉）的白色大理石。他利用了用取芯过程中的废弃材料，然后使用树脂帮助稳定，使花瓶像是悬空在玻璃里，而大理石表面细微的纹路也更清晰。彩色的花朵或糖果放置其中，在庄重典雅的大理石对比下能更突显。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154056Y0x8hrji1AtGbNeB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154056fMHRNzdGy3KChgwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154057xYIFV2BTPdkRXb1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154057UzYp3Q9ZgyChPrJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154057WNZOhpASmIlrXzPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>harto系列家具</h2>\n<p>法国家具品牌 harto 推出的家具参加了巴黎家居装饰博览会和科隆家具展。这组家具都以浅色的木材为主体，点缀以有趣的彩色，年轻而活泼。除了颜色外，家具的形状也使用了活泼的元素。餐具柜门上采用了倾斜的纹路，有点像船帆，挂壁式隔板设计成上小下大的梯形，比普通的柜子则增加了一份轻巧灵活。<a href=\"http://www.hartodesign.fr\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154058ILYi5OHmczhwNsV8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154059JBKz53smItwvEy9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45721271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154059ot41WMnugSAkzEKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154100FPnOTCBWoav2J5GU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45721271\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541003dKzhOU8JPWlx7Ap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154101lUapIJ6rndABekWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Star Wars by nendo</h2>\n<p>这是 Nendo 推出的星球大战周边，他们以球体为基础，制作了不同的人物造型。简化后的形象只保留了最具识别度的元素，表面有凹凸纹理或附加的配件，小巧可爱。这种模块化的设计可以被运用在很多领域，首饰挂坠，小玩具，餐具如调料盒。它的有趣的延展是 nendo 的一种探索。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/star-wars-2/?erelease\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154101uy8rNjlpF5kVGXd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154102tAUFNRQoVX58fLWZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541028tzep4IhDgrYu2KX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154103ru5zB4cHIhx8dbks.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154103OcV7wdXpMs49oGFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154104dygObTQWqVXIctRY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mike Bultje by Lignum Bike Company</h2>\n<p>这些挂在墙上的木头工具都是帮助将自行车挂在墙上的，Lignum Bike Company 从自行车结构的各个部位出发，开发了一系列工具，或者是拖出车架或座杆的柜子，或者是一根安放轮胎的横木，而用皮条将脚踏板夹住，一些柜子还有放配件的功能。横挂在墙上的自行车有一份工业美感，这组设计产自加拿大，<a href=\"https://lignumbike.com/get-it-on-the-wall-shop-now/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715410459rnGke3jqdSNi1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154105SAqn04o7iLcVrBa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154105tTjGfHEaVOz3dp8J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154105vwhmCZe3anS9I5t1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77961019\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154106liA3QY4LCXBt7ZJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“wings” by haim evgi</h2>\n<p>以色列设计师从鸟的翅膀出发设计了这组小鸟灯。它的侧面是细长的等腰梯形，两个斜面掏空，让灯光从两头出来。灯罩是微微倾斜的，恰如小鸟斜立的姿态，简单优美。这款灯的灯罩是橡木制作的，方向可调，里面有一个灯泡。有吊灯、台灯和落地灯多种。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154107SynRrAGNXKuBD2Fw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154107DYQAlRkW3wGU9c1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154107hQpTz590lYIHZtiJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154108DLyqVIB3kijuzCe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541080T7kbDH5hr3juneP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mandarin natural chocolate bars by Yuta Takahashi </h2>\n<p>这是日本平面设计师  Yuta Takahashi  带来的巧克力包装，他将包装设计成信件的样式。正反两面是纯白色的，只有非常少的黑色印刷体文字，清晰而诗意。Mandarin Natural Chocolate 宣称只使用有机可可和蔗糖，极简的包装也表现出天然和纯粹。一些隐藏信息蕴含其中，比如下面一排黑点有 10 个，代表了可可的浓度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154109g7kLxuftbTyil15d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154109V4IF85JqUol7Mu0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77136752\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154110r0o8egbsMnFUHJ1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541106KPWD3szR8ZnjbN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154111D498XS0liERzecCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}